lead_paragraph: Prince Fielder and Mitch Moreland are two prominent power sources for Texas, and that's why they've stayed in manager Jeff Banister's lineup through some long droughts.

headline.print_headline: Struggling Fielder, Moreland Lead Rangers Past Pirates 6-2
